title: Listfinite - Shopping List
summary: List keeping app with Android wear support!
description: Listfinite is a easy to use shopping list,  just swipe items away as you get them from the store.  Any device using android 4.0+ should be supported.    Beta Android wear support.  If there are any problems let me know what device you are using and I will see what can be done.
descriptionHTML: Listfinite is a easy to use shopping list,  just swipe items away as you get them from the store.  Any device using android 4.0+ should be supported.    Beta Android wear support.  If there are any problems let me know what device you are using and I will see what can be done.
comments: Best list app in a while ^
Grocery list This app is awesomely made! It has all the typical categories and you can even make your own, not to mention you can pick your favorites!! I like how precise you can be with it :)
Wow! What an awesome application! So practical and easy to use!
